These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, january
City: hannover, berlin
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, grey
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, social-worker
House: tower, craftsman
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
5. the social-worker is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Birthday      | november   | january        |
| City          | berlin    | hannover     |
| Color         | grey | ivory   |
| Job           | doctor  | social-worker |
| House   | tower   | craftsman       |
| Game           | billiard   | mah-jongg      |

