.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, animation
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, oliveros
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating broccoli is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | romance       | animation      |
| Food          | asparagus   | broccoli |
| Flower         | iris | daffodil  |
| Sport   | sailing        | basketball     |
| Transport   | airplane       | quad-bike   |
| Cigar           | fonseca        | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, reading
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower
City: san-francisco, new-york
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the game-smoker##1
3. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Game      | go      | mah-jongg   |
| Hobby         | gardening | reading |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | game    |
| Flower   | sunflower | marigold  |
| City         | san-francisco      | new-york  |
| Pet     | rabbit    | lizard     |

